      <title>聯合國安理會對蘇丹北達爾富爾地區即將發生的攻擊表示關注</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/un-security-council-concerned-over-imminent-attack-sudans-north-darfur-2024-04-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[聯合國安理會週六對快速支援部隊（RSF）即將對蘇丹北達爾富爾地區的法希爾發動攻擊表示「深切關注」。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/un-security-council-concerned-over-imminent-attack-sudans-north-darfur-2024-04-27/</guid>
