      <title>塔斯社稱，俄羅斯拘留了被捕副部長的下屬</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-holds-custody-subordinate-arrested-deputy-minister-tass-says-2024-04-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[據塔斯社週六報道，國防部長謝爾蓋·紹伊古的盟友因涉嫌受賄被捕，俄羅斯一家法院已下令拘留另一名嫌疑人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-holds-custody-subordinate-arrested-deputy-minister-tass-says-2024-04-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 18:42:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
